_:Nf24978d51b5f4b9ead1391ca5f60ba34 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Nigel Minns became Regional Director for the East Midlands in March 2026.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously a Director of Children’s Services for 8 years and held a national role with the Association of Directors of Children’s Services.</p>\n\n<p>Nigel began his career as a primary school teacher and has also worked with the Office of the Regional Schools Commissioner as an external deputy director.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
